### 多项式开平方根

给你一个$n-1$次多项式$F(x)$，让你求出一个多项式$G(x)$，使得

$$G^{2}(x)\equiv F(x)\pmod{x^{n}}$$

牛顿迭代吼啊！

$$A(G)=G^{2}-F$$

$$A^{\prime}(G)=2G$$

$$\begin{aligned}
G&\equiv G_{0}-\cfrac{A(G_{0})}{A{^\prime}(G_{0})}\\
&\equiv G_{0}-\cfrac{G_{0}^{2}-F}{2G_{0}}\\
&\equiv\cfrac{G_{0}^{2}+F}{2G_{0}}\\
&=\cfrac{1}{2}(G_{0}+\cfrac{F}{G_{0}})\pmod{x^{2t}}
\end{aligned}$$

